---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Faq from '../../components/Faq.astro';

const article = { author: "Eliot Nash", authorId: "eliot-nash", authorTitle: "Market & Real Estate Analyst", publishDate: "2026-05-13", modifiedDate: "2026-05-13", section: "City Guides" };
const topics = ["city", "market"];
const faqPageJsonLd = JSON.stringify({"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": [{"@type": "Question", "name": "Are there cannabis dispensaries in Rockland, Maine?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Rockland has at least 3 active dispensaries: Highbrow (recreational, 696 Main St), Scrimshaw Cannabis (medical, 500 Main St, 207-466-9408), and Botany (recreational at 403 Main St and medical at 161 High St, Belfast)."}}]});
---
<Layout title="Rockland, Maine Dispensary Guide — Highbrow, Scrimshaw, Botany 2026" description="Rockland, Maine dispensary guide. 3 dispensaries: Highbrow (rec), Scrimshaw Cannabis (med), and Botany (rec+med) on Main Street for 2026." heroImage="/images/heroes/rockland-dispensary-guide.jpg" article={article} topics={topics} >
<style>
  article{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}.article-header{margin-bottom:2.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)}.subtitle{font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--color-text-light)}section{margin-bottom:2.5rem}section h2,section h3{margin-top:1.5rem}section h2:first-child{margin-top:0}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:1rem 0}th,td{padding:0.6rem .75rem;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)}th{background:var(--color-background)}ul,ol{padding-left:1.5rem}li{margin-bottom:.4rem}.disclaimer{background:var(--color-disclaimer-bg);border:1px solid var(--color-disclaimer-border);padding:1rem;border-radius:.5rem;font-size:.875rem;color:var(--color-disclaimer-text)}.fact-box{background:rgba(88,129,87,.1);padding:1.75rem;border-radius:1rem;border-left:4px solid var(--color-primary)}.fact-box h2{margin-top:0;font-size:1.25rem}.fact-box table{margin:0}.further-reading{background:rgba(88,129,87,.05);padding:1.5rem;border-radius:1rem;margin-top:3rem}.further-reading h2{margin-top:0;font-size:1.25rem}
</style>

<article>
  <div class="article-header"><h1>Rockland, ME Dispensary Guide</h1><p class="subtitle">Three dispensaries on Main Street — Rockland's thriving Midcoast cannabis market</p></div>

  <section class="fact-box"><h2>Rockland Cannabis Quick Facts</h2>
    <table aria-label="Rockland cannabis market overview">
      <thead><tr><th scope="col">Fact</th><th scope="col">Details</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><strong>Medical Legal</strong></td><td>Yes</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Recreational Legal</strong></td><td>Yes — town permits</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Dispensaries in Town</strong></td><td>3 confirmed active</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Known Dispensaries</strong></td><td>Highbrow (rec, 696 Main), Scrimshaw Cannabis (med, 500 Main), Botany (rec 403 Main)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Population</strong></td><td>~7,100 (2020 Census)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>County</strong></td><td>Knox County</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section><h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Rockland is the commercial heart of Midcoast Maine's Knox County and supports three active dispensaries — making it one of the most densely served small towns in the region for cannabis access. All three cluster along or near Main Street, creating a walkable corridor that serves Rockland's ~7,100 year-round residents plus the arts-community and harbor tourism traffic.</p>
  </section>

  <section><h2>Highbrow — Recreational</h2>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> 696 Main Street, Rockland, ME<br><strong>Type:</strong> Recreational (21+)</p>
    <p>Highbrow is a statewide operator with multiple Maine locations (Rockland, Bath, Augusta, Portland, Manchester). Their classification system (Uplifted, Balanced, Relaxed) simplifies the shopping experience for first-time buyers. They partner with Maine craft growers including Hazy Hill, Rugged Roots, and Paul's Boutique for flower, plus house-made concentrates and edibles.</p>

    <h3>Scrimshaw Cannabis — Medical</h3>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> 500 Main Street, Rockland, ME<br><strong>Phone:</strong> (207) 466-9408<br><strong>Hours:</strong> Daily 11am-6pm<br><strong>Type:</strong> Medical</p>
    <p>Scrimshaw Cannabis serves Knox County's medical patient community from its Main Street storefront. They carry flower, concentrates, edibles, and medical-grade products.</p>

    <h3>Botany — Recreational + Medical</h3>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> 403 Main Street, Rockland, ME (rec); 161 High Street, Belfast, ME (med)<br><strong>Type:</strong> Recreational in Rockland, Medical in Belfast</p>
    <p>Botany is a Midcoast-focused operator with recreational storefront on Main Street, Rockland and medical operation in Belfast (161 High St). Their five-category feeling system (Up, Relaxed, Focused, Social, Balanced) helps customers choose by intended effect rather than strain name.</p>
  </section>

  <section><h2>Nearby Dispensary Options</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Camden (~5 mi north):</strong> No dispensaries in Camden — Rockland is the nearest option</li>
      <li><strong>Belfast (~8 mi south):</strong> Stones Throw Cannabis (medical), Botany (medical, 161 High St)</li>
      <li><strong>Damariscotta (~12 mi northeast):</strong> Cannabis Cured (rec), Above & Beyond Cannabis (med)</li>
      <li><strong>Bath (~17 mi west):</strong> Highbrow (rec + med), Sinsemilla (rec)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="further-reading"><h2>Related Guides</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/guides/camden-dispensary-guide">Camden Dispensary Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/belfast-dispensary-guide">Belfast Dispensary Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/damariscotta-dispensary-guide">Damariscotta Dispensary Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/augusta-dispensary-guide">Augusta Dispensary Guide</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <Faq questions={[
      { q: "Are there dispensaries in Rockland, Maine?", a: "Yes. Rockland has 3 active dispensaries: Highbrow (rec, 696 Main), Scrimshaw Cannabis (med, 500 Main), and Botany (rec, 403 Main)." },
      { q: "Which is the best dispensary in Rockland?", a: "Rockland offers variety: Highbrow for the widest selection and statewide brand recognition, Scrimshaw for focused medical patient service, and Botany for their effect-based product classification system." },
      { q: "Does Rockland accept out-of-state medical cards?", a: "Maine allows reciprocity. Contact Scrimshaw Cannabis and Botany directly about current reciprocity policies." },
    ]} />
  </section>

  <p class="disclaimer"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Information is provided for general reference only. Always verify details directly with the dispensary.</p>
</article>
</Layout>
<script type="application/ld+json" set:text={faqPageJsonLd} is:inline></script>